ask user if they want to play the game
store answer in usercontinue
if the usercontinue equals no 
  stop program
while usercontinue equals yes
generate a random number between 1 and 100
set attempts to 7
while attempts is greater that 0
ask user to guess the number
store the guess
if users guess equals winning number
  print winning message
  set attempts to 0
else
  subtract 1 from attempts
end while
if user did not guess the number
  print losing message
  print correct number
ask user if they want to play again
store answer in usercontinue
end while
